<div class="jumbotron">
  <h2>Hello, Fellow Pathfinders!</h2>
  <p>Looking for a creative way to remember your characters?</p>
  <p>From the HeroLab character management software, save your favorite character as a XML File. Upload that file and click, "Create Deck". Use the resulting file to "Generate Cards"</p>

  <div align="center">
    <span><h4>Consider making a contribution</h4></span>
    <%= form_tag charges_path do %>
      <article>
        <% if flash[:error].present? %>
          <div id="error_explanation">
            <p><%= flash[:error] %></p>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </article>
      <script src="https://checkout.stripe.com/checkout.js" class="stripe-button"
              data-label="Donate $5.00"
              data-key="<%= Rails.configuration.stripe[:publishable_key] %>"
              data-description="Your donations keep this project alive"
              data-amount="500"
              data-panel-label="Donate"
              data-locale="auto"></script>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>